Date: Sat, 21 Mar 2026 05:24:15 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: IndexedDB storage layer (PlatformDB) replacing
 Firestore

- PlatformDB: full IndexedDB abstraction with 8 object stores
  (projects, categories, corpus, strategy, demand, deep_dive, app_state, cache)
- Scope completion persists project + category + corpus to IndexedDB
- Strategy runner saves corpus and output to IndexedDB for project categories
- Hard reset clears IndexedDB alongside localStorage
- Zero Firebase dependency for platform-v1 project flow
- All data scoped by projectId/categoryId for clean isolation
